review_data.title: Supper
review_data.content: Alles wird frisch vor unseren Augen zubereitet, Grosse Auswahl und günstige Preise. Ich kann es nur weiter empfehlen supper.

review_data.title: Great food, good prices, good service
review_data.content: Located in the heart of langstrasse, this is a regular place where myself and some friends go. They offer a wide variety of Turkish foods it all seems very fresh and very tasty.
